README

Transforms the output of Ripper.sexp into simple XML via Nokogiri, giving you access to the whole XML toolchain, including CSS selectors, XPath, and XSLT.

$ bundle exec pry -r './ylyn.rb'

> puts Ylyn.new('class Foo ; end').css('const_ref').to_xml

<const_ref>
  <_const value="Foo" location="1 6"/>
</const_ref>
